Package dev.bjdelacruz.models

Class ChamorroDictionaryEntry

java.lang.Object
dev.bjdelacruz.models.ChamorroDictionaryEntry
public final class ChamorroDictionaryEntry extends Object
Represents a dictionary entry or a record in a table that contains a Chamorro word, its pronunciation, the English translation, its etymology, some examples, and any notes.
